data.name: Emperor Maju Garzett
data.desc: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must be Special Summoned (from your hand) by Tributing 3 monsters. This card's ATK becomes the combined original ATK of the Tributed monsters. Your opponent cannot activate cards or effects during the Battle Phase.
